110
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:11,119
kind of chore or low-level task, you

111
00:03:09,598 --> 00:03:12,877
start to build up some productive

112
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:14,640
momentum. you get your brain into work

113
00:03:12,878 --> 00:03:16,719
mode and that momentum can carry you

114
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:18,639
into that more challenging task that you

115
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:19,839
were procrastinating on earlier. So, if

116
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:21,199
you're not the kind of person who can

117
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,560
start doing your most challenging work

118
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:24,158
first thing in the morning, I think you

119
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:26,080
should try to integrate that process of

120
00:03:24,158 --> 00:03:27,919
building productive momentum right into

121
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:29,680
your daily schedule. And you do that by

122
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:30,718
building a morning routine. Now, we'll

123
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,920
definitely talk more about morning

124
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:33,679
routines in the future, and I'll be

125
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:35,119
sharing mine with you in detail. But to

126
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:36,720
get you started, if you don't have a

127
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:38,399
morning routine right now, sit down with

128
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:39,998
a piece of paper and create a list of

129
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:41,679
three to five habits that you'll do when

130
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:43,120
you wake up first thing in the morning.

131
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:44,479
And these things can be easy, but the

132
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:46,080
key is that they start to build up some

133
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:47,439
of that productive momentum and get you

134
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:48,878
ready for the day. So, they can be

135
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:50,559
things like meditating, cooking

136
00:03:48,878 --> 00:03:52,317
breakfast, going for a walk, or going to

137
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:54,399
the gym. Really, anything that kind of

138
00:03:52,318 --> 00:03:55,518
gets you in a productive mindset. Now,

139
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,719
whether you're that kind of person who

140
00:03:55,519 --> 00:03:57,999
can roll out of bed and start working

